sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 客户端 (React/PixiJS)
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant Handler as GameLogicHandler
    participant SM as SessionManager
    participant NPC as NpcManager
    participant Shop as ShopSystem
    participant EQ as EquipmentManager
    participant SK as SkillManager
    participant CO as CombatSystem
    participant DB as Database

    Note over Client,DB: === NPC 商店购买流程 ===
    Client->>WS: CallNPCPacket(npc_id)
    WS->>Handler: on_call_npc(session_id, payload)
    Handler->>SM: get_state(session_id)
    Handler->>NPC: get_npcs_near(map_id, x, y, range)
    NPC-->>Handler: Vec&lt;NpcTemplate&gt;
    Handler->>SM: update_state(current_npc_id=npc.id)
    Handler-->>WS: NPCGoodsPacket(goods_list)
    WS-->>Client: NPCGoods [物品列表+价格]
    
    Client->>WS: BuyItemPacket(npc_id, item_id, count)
    WS->>Handler: on_buy_item(session_id, payload)
    Handler->>NPC: get_template(npc_id)
    Handler->>Shop: buy_item(npc, template, gold, inventory)
    Shop-->>Handler: ShopResult::Success
    Handler->>SM: update_state(gold=new_gold)
    Handler-->>WS: GainedItemPacket(item_id, name)
    Handler-->>WS: LoseGoldPacket(price)
    WS-->>Client: GainedItem + LoseGold
    Note over Client: UI更新背包 & 金币

    Note over Client,DB: === 装备穿戴流程 ===
    Client->>WS: MoveItemPacket(from_slot=inv, to_slot=equip)
    WS->>Handler: on_move_item(session_id, payload)
    Handler->>SM: get_state(session_id)
    Handler->>EQ: equip(inv_slot, item, template)
    EQ-->>Handler: EquipmentResult::Success
    EQ->>EQ: calculate_stats(level, item_manager)
    EQ-->>Handler: PlayerStats
    Handler->>SM: update_state(equipment=...)
    Handler-->>WS: EquipSlotItemPacket(slot, item_info)
    Handler-->>WS: BaseStatsInfoPacket(stats)
    WS-->>Client: EquipSlotItem + BaseStatsInfo
    Note over Client: UI更新装备位 & 属性面板

    Note over Client,DB: === 技能使用流程（火球术） ===
    Client->>WS: MagicKeyPacket(spell=FireBall, direction)
    WS->>Handler: on_magic_key(session_id, payload)
    Handler->>SM: get_state(session_id)
    Handler->>SK: use_skill(FireBall, &current_mp)
    SK-->>Handler: SkillResult::Success
    Note over SK: 熟练度+1~3
    SK->>SK: 检查是否升级
    
    alt 技能升级
        SK-->>Handler: SkillLeveled(FireBall, Lv2)
        Handler-->>WS: MagicLeveledPacket(FireBall, Lv2, prof)
    end
    
    Handler->>CO: player_attack_monster(stats, target, ...)
    CO->>CO: damage = fireball_damage(mc, skill_level)
    CO-->>Handler: AttackResult
    
    Handler-->>WS: MagicCastPacket(object_id, FireBall, target)
    Handler-->>WS: DamageIndicatorPacket(target, damage, Hit)
    WS-->>Client: MagicCast + DamageIndicator
    Note over Client: 渲染火球动画 & 伤害飘字

    Note over Client,DB: === 安全区回血（Tick循环） ===
    loop Every 10 ticks
        Handler->>SM: get_states_on_map(map_id)
        SM-->>Handler: Vec&lt;SessionState&gt;
        loop each player
            alt player in safe_zone
                Handler->>SM: update_state(hp=min(max_hp, hp+regen))
            end
        end
        Handler-->>WS: HealthChangedPacket(hp, mp)
    end

    Note over Client,DB: === 死亡处理流程 ===
    CO->>CO: monster_attack_player → player HP <= 0
    CO-->>Handler: AttackResult(target_alive=false)
    Handler->>SM: update_state(current_hp=0)
    Handler-->>WS: DeathPacket(player_id)
    Handler-->>WS: HealthChangedPacket(0, mp)
    
    WS-->>Client: Death
    Note over Client: 显示死亡画面
    
    Client->>WS: TownRevivePacket (回城复活)
    WS->>Handler: on_town_revive(session_id)
    Handler->>SM: update_state(hp=max_hp/2, map_id=0, location=safe_zone)
    Handler-->>WS: UserInformationPacket (复活信息)
    Handler-->>WS: MapChangedPacket(map_0)
    WS-->>Client: UserInformation + MapChanged
    Note over Client: UI恢复 & 地图加载
